The town is falling, due to coldness. 
Shinoka holds the last fire in town. He is the last hope to overcome winter, but he's dying. 
Wassabi is a boy looking for warmness. He doesn't want his town to be destroyed by winter.
Wassabi is talented, not just in warmness, but also in coldness.
Xincu are prepared for feast, coldness is their food, and the town is their dinning table. 